Barzyna  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Rychliki, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  east of Rychliki,  south-east of Elbląg, and  west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
